frames.caption: A couple stands closely together, taking a selfie with a scenic rocky coastline in the background. The woman wears a colorful hooded jacket, while the man is dressed in a gray coat. Behind them, waves crash against the rugged cliffs under a cloudy sky.
frames.description: The scene captures a couple enjoying a moment by a dramatic coastal landscape. The rocky cliffs and turbulent sea create a striking natural backdrop, suggesting a location known for its scenic beauty.

frames.caption: A couple is captured mid-jump near the edge of a scenic cliff overlooking the ocean. The woman wears a colorful beanie and a long black coat, while the man is dressed in a gray jacket and jeans. The dramatic backdrop features rugged cliffs and a choppy sea under an overcast sky.
frames.description: The scene is set on a grassy cliffside overlooking the ocean, with two people joyfully jumping near the edge. The setting is natural and dramatic, with rocky cliffs and a turbulent sea creating a striking contrast against the cloudy sky.
